<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Discount Coupon</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .gift-icon {
            font-size: 64px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .coupon-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border: 3px dashed #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
        }
        
        .discount-label {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .discount-amount {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin: 10px 0;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .coupon-code {
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 2px dashed #667eea;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        
        .copy-hint {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .details-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        
        .detail-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            color: #666;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .expiry-warning {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffc107;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: #856404;
        }
        
        .expiry-warning strong {
            color: #d32f2f;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 16px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.5);
        }
        
        .how-to-use {
            background: #e8eaf6;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .how-to-use h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .steps {
            list-style: none;
            counter-reset: step-counter;
        }
        
        .steps li {
            counter-increment: step-counter;
            margin: 12px 0;
            padding-left: 35px;
            position: relative;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .steps li:before {
            content: counter(step-counter);
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 24px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        
        .social-links {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .social-links a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 20px 10px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .discount-amount {
                font-size: 36px;
            }
            
            .coupon-code {
                font-size: 20px;
                letter-spacing: 2px;
                padding: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="gift-icon">üéÅ</div>
            <h1>Special Discount Just for You!</h1>
            <p>You've been rewarded with an exclusive coupon</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
            
            <p class="message">
                Great news! We're excited to offer you an exclusive discount on your next purchase. 
                We value your loyalty and want to show our appreciation with this special offer.
            </p>
            
            <!-- Coupon Box -->
            <div class="coupon-box">
                <div class="discount-label">Your Discount</div>
                <div class="discount-amount">{{discountPercentage}}% OFF</div>
                <div class="coupon-code">{{code}}</div>
                <div class="copy-hint">üìã Copy this code and use it at checkout</div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Expiry Warning -->
            <div class="expiry-warning">
                ‚è∞ <strong>Hurry!</strong> This coupon expires on <strong>{{expirationDate}}</strong>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Details -->
            <div class="details-box">
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Discount:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{discountPercentage}}% OFF</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Coupon Code:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{code}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Valid Until:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{expirationDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Status:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value" style="color: #4caf50;">‚úì Active</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- CTA Button -->
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/products" class="cta-button">
                    üõí Start Shopping Now
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <!-- How to Use -->
            <div class="how-to-use">
                <h3>üéØ How to Use Your Coupon</h3>
                <ul class="steps">
                    <li>Browse our amazing products and add items to your cart</li>
                    <li>Proceed to checkout when you're ready</li>
                    <li>Enter the coupon code <strong>{{code}}</strong> in the discount field</li>
                    <li>Watch your total price drop by {{discountPercentage}}%!</li>
                    <li>Complete your purchase and enjoy your savings</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p class="message">
                This is our way of saying thank you for being an amazing customer. 
                Don't let this opportunity slip away ‚Äì your discount is waiting! üéâ
            </p>
            
            <p class="message" style="margin-top: 30px;">
                <strong>Need help?</strong> Our customer support team is always here to assist you. 
                Feel free to reach out if you have any questions.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>XroboFly E-Commerce</strong></p>
            <p>Your trusted online shopping destination</p>
            
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> | 
                <a href="#">Terms of Service</a> | 
                <a href="#">Contact Us</a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
                ¬© {{year}} XroboFly. All rights reserved.
            </p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 11px; color: #aaa;">
                You received this email because you have an account with XroboFly.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
